name: CMS
body:
### Welcome to CMS.
This is basically a complete system for the Sugar Cane managment in java. The actual way of design is running the java code in a nano server which in turn supplies the code back to the internet. Where a user can access it from website.


### Authors and Contributors
The authors are Guru Dhanush , Akhil Jayadev, Mukund Varma, Akhilesh, Nishit.
